The logi-loader tool acts as a serial loader for the logibone Mark-1 board when plugged into the 
beaglebone expansion port.
Usage:
logi_loader <bitfile>.bit

The tool can only be executed after running the mux setting script for your board (logibon or mark1).

Install:

execute the "make" command in the folder
execute the "make install" command as root user to copy the tool to /usr/bin

